You are high and exalted
And worthy of praise;
With our hearts
We will love and adore.

You are high and exalted
And worthy of praise;
Holy is the Lord.
Holy is the Lord.

Holy, Holy,
Holy is the Lord;
Holy, Holy,
Holy is the Lord.

